ed audibly, as I imagined the scene in my head. As for whether"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I was into it or not... the answer was of course a yes."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Senpai"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Oh, are you one of us too? Great, that makes it way easier."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Senpai"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["On that note, I cleaned the lounge up as much as I could but, could"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["you go and give it a once over? Maybe my eyes missed something."]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[100]},{"code":213,"indent":0,"parameters":[2,9,true]},{"code":221,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":204,"indent":0,"parameters":[8,14,4,true]},{"code":203,"indent":0,"parameters":[2,0,19,4,0]},{"code":222,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":213,"indent":0,"parameters":[2,8,true]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I looked around the lounge, and it was really well cleaned."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["To think there were people doing it here just a bit ago..."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I can't find a trace even after knowing about it."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Afterwards, I continued to work hard at my job, even as I chatted"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["with senpai from time to time."]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[100]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"blace",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":232,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,0,0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0,30,true,0]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["...It's not like this is a regular gathering spot for cute girls though,"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[